headline: Ronald S. Lauder to Retire from The Estée Lauder Companies’ Board of Directors
summary: NEW YORK, January 10, 2025--The Estée Lauder Companies (NYSE: EL) announced today that Ronald S. Lauder will retire from the Company’s Board of Directors (the "Board") effective immediately. Pursuant to the stockholders’ agreement among Lauder family members and the Company, Mr. Lauder has the right to designate two directors of the Company.
